19#include "ODUPCEANReader.h"
20
21namespace ZXing {
22namespace OneD {
23
24/**
25* <p>Implements decoding of the UPC-E format.</p>
26* <p><a href="http://www.barcodeisland.com/upce.phtml">This</a> is a great reference for
27* UPC-E information.</p>
28*
29* @author Sean Owen
30*/
31class UPCEReader : public UPCEANReader
32{
33public:
34 explicit UPCEReader(const DecodeHints& hints) : UPCEANReader(hints) {}
35
36protected:
37 BarcodeFormat expectedFormat() const override;
38 BitArray::Range decodeMiddle(const BitArray& row, BitArray::Iterator, std::string& resultString) const override;
39 bool checkChecksum(const std::string& s) const override;
40 BitArray::Range decodeEnd(const BitArray& row, BitArray::Iterator begin) const override;
41};
42
43} // OneD
44} // ZXing
